        <p data-role="text">All work&#xAD;sta&#xAD;tions come with safety re&#xAD;minders, in&#xAD;clud&#xAD;ing stay&#xAD;ing at least six feet (1.8m) apart and walk&#xAD;ing clock&#xAD;wise in the of&#xAD;fice, so that em&#xAD;ploy&#xAD;ees can do their part to keep their of&#xAD;fice safe.</p>
